<item>
            <title>[LU-8103] Interop master&lt;-&gt;2.8.0 : sanity test_404: deactivate error</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8103</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f7c94bb4-0e2a-11e6-9b34-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f7c94bb4-0e2a-11e6-9b34-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_404 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;deactivate error
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 404: validate manual {de}activated works properly for OSPs ============================ 12:13:13 (1461845593)
CMD: trevis-27vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl dl
Deactivate:  lustre-OST0000-osc-MDT0000
CMD: trevis-27vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl --device %lustre-OST0000-osc-MDT0000 deactivate
CMD: trevis-27vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl dl
CMD: trevis-27vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl dl
  8 UP osp lustre-OST0000-osc-MDT0000 lustre-MDT0000-mdtlov_UUID 5
 sanity test_404: @@@@@@ FAIL: deactivate error 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This issue can be traced back to  build# 3352 on master from where it first started occuring.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Server: 2.8.0 , build# 12, EL7.2 &lt;br/&gt;
Client: master, build# 3356 , EL 7.2</environment>
